/*
  wikimyei.inference.expected_value.mdn.bnf
  ==============================================
  Fresh node-centered ExpectedValue MDN surface.

  <mdn-file> ::= "MDN" "{" <kv-list> "}"
  <kv-list>  ::= (<key> "=" <value> ";")*

  Required keys:
    VERSION = wikimyei.inference.expected_value.mdn.v1
    COMPONENT_ID
    INPUT_REPRESENTATION_ID
    TARGET_DOMAIN = node_future
    TARGET_COORDS = 0,1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8
    MIXTURE_COUNT
    HIDDEN_WIDTH

  Optional keys:
    TARGET_MASK_POLICY = all_target_features_valid
    ACTIVITY_TARGET = node_feature_support_mean
    HEAD_POLICY = per_node
    CONTEXT_REDUCTION = last | mean
    RESIDUAL_DEPTH = integer >= 0
    SIGMA_MIN = float >= 0
    SIGMA_MAX = float >= 0, 0 disables
    EPS = float > 0

  V1 predicts the target-side future NodeLift tensor:
    future_node_features [B,C,Hf,N,9]
  under:
    future_node_mask [B,C,Hf,N,9].

  Future edge tensors remain source evidence for target-side NodeLift and
  diagnostics. They are not the MDN target.
*/
